     The OIG Hotline provides a prompt, effective channel for Department
      employees and contract personnel, as well as private citizens, to
      report incidents of waste, fraud, abuse and mismanagement in the
     Department of State and the Broadcasting Board of Governors to the
            Inspector General. For more information, click here.
